# Akka Actors Remoting example
All credit goes to the folks at Typesafe

  A sample for the Typesafe Stack (http://typesafe.com/stack).
  Akka 2.0 sample project using Scala and SBT.
  To run and test it use SBT invoke: 'sbt run'

## Getting started
Also see http://typesafe.com/stack/download#osx

### JDK 1.6+
Obviously needed.

###Homebrew - package manager for osx
http://http://mxcl.github.com/homebrew/
$ ruby <(curl -fsSkL raw.github.com/mxcl/homebrew/go)

###Eclipse scala integration
http://scala-ide.org/download/current.html
http://download.scala-ide.org/releases-29/stable/site

